Customer Segment:
   Description:  
     * Our company will be targeting local businesses in the Omaha area.
     * We provide reviews for various businesses for the customers to read. 
   Needs: 
     * The customer is looking for restaurants, venues etc. in the Omaha area that they would like to know more about 
     or would like to go to. 
     * The customer is also seeking a unique and excellent experience with our reviews and with the businesses themselves.
   Solution: 
     * Our company is in charge of helping local businesses gain more customers by providing reviews on various types of 
        social media. 
     * As the company grows, we will be aware of the businesses being able to reach out to us and help improve our company
     while we improve theirs.
     
